{"tid":710244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲智庫民調「可信賴的世界領導人」","createTime":"2018-06-20T14:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T16:17:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d4259b18af27134326c7cc4e07cc9f9c8dbd87","tid":710244,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"澳洲智庫民調「可信賴的世界領導人」 川普排在...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2464333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2464333&d=gVBwHMV%2BUKRpFY4WJToIjZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=09709c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2464333&h=36c3e969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2464333</a><br />\n<br />\n2018-06-20 22:43<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕澳洲智庫針對「可信賴的外國」和「可信賴的世界領導人」的調查結果顯示，澳洲人最信賴英國和英國首相梅伊（Theresa May），而<span style=\"color: red;\">美國總統川普（Donald Trump）的排名甚至比中國國家主席習近平還要低。</span><br />\n<br />\n《共同社》報導，澳洲獨立智庫「洛伊國際政策研究所」（Lowy Institute）這項民調訪問了1200人，今（20）日公布的調查結果顯示，在「可信賴的外國」中，英國位居第 1，第2名是日本，第3名以下依序為法國、印度、美國、中國。<br />\n<br />\n在「可信賴的世界領導人」中，英相梅伊排在榜首，其次是日本首相安倍晉三，澳洲總理滕博爾（Malcolm Turnbull）排在第3名，接著是法國總統馬克宏（Emmanuel Macron）、習近平、印度總理莫迪（Narendra Modi），川普排在第7名。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，對川普感到不滿的人佔了70%，雖然川普人氣不佳，但澳洲人仍持續支持澳洲與美國維持穩固的同盟關係。認為與美國同盟關係重要的人有76%，雖比去年減少1%，但基本上持平。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">針對近年在澳洲影響力增加的中國，「是經濟夥伴還是軍事威脅」，有82%回答前者。不過，有72%受訪者認為「政府過度批准來自中國的投資」，比2014年大增16%。</span>"},{"pid":"fe8f19f83366e87faed9fdf6eb067160b35f0a66","tid":710244,"uid":170772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"等睇澳豬淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b35bdd833f409b207f0912df97ebb24320c638","tid":710244,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"文翠珊都有得吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed76140dcfa83b5e23fda33ba1ecd6c635da247","tid":710244,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:33:53.000Z","msg":"1200人睇世界領導人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9bd506a7bd2910d0b9db8c1650cf9c18b2201d","tid":710244,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"174882aecc1e135748847431464aeb5efbb376ec","tid":710244,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"為咗踩侵可在去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286c79db241fd91bab09aae1e9e938af0645cb6d","tid":710244,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"昨日中國澳門 今日中國澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc95fda8b41f0682ec47d2161a7f4dbfc85338c","tid":710244,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"1200人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過香港2大祖國排頭<br />\n德國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fb0d7eea4525a383811d7dae86e44accd358a8","tid":710244,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dc95fda8b41f0682ec47d2161a7f4dbfc85338c","tid":710244,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"1200人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過香港2大祖國排頭<br />\n德國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gi